joiner-mover-leaver.md

## Identity Lifecycle Management

### Joiner

- User created via IAM

- Assigned role based on department

- MFA enforced on first login

### Mover

- Role access reviewed and updated

- Previous permissions removed

- Change documented for audit purposes

### Leaver

- Access disabled immediately

- Keys and tokens revoked

- User removed from all groups

- Evidence retained for compliance
